  "notes": "react-toastify variables exposed globally. The Relay app overrides toast.background and text colors via Toastify__toast--theme--light; Relay does NOT use the rainbow progress gradient by default. Use these only when rendering Toastify-driven notifications; for app-native banners use --color-background-fill-{success|warning|info|critical}."
